com.nsqre.insquare.User

Class InSquareProfile

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.nsqre.insquare.User.InSquareProfile

  • public class InSquareProfile
extends java.lang.Object
    InSquareProfile is the class that handles most of the user data. It's a singleton class which stores user's data locally, so the app can react faster to inputs and has less data to request from the backend
